    "4111117": {
        "Desc": "",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "Allan",
                    "T": "Phew! I thought I was going to die here..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Draff",
                    "T": "You fool! What were you thinking, gallivanting off on your own at a time like this!?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Allan",
                    "T": "I—I'm sorry! I'll never do it again!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Draff",
                    "T": "I sincerely apologize for the trouble Allan has caused for you all. I will make absolutely sure that he learns his lesson!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Yeah, next time you think about doing something stupid, think again!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "The meteorite is just over there."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Paimon's gonna go take a closer loo— Huh? Princess, your <color=#00E1FFFF>Vision</color> is <color=#00E1FFFF>flashing</color>!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Fischl",
                    "T": "Oh? Could it be, perchance, that mine Edelstein der Dunkelheit portends the certain demise of this unholy hex of cold?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Maybe...? What kind of things does your Vision react to, exactly?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Fischl",
                    "T": "The profoundest of enigmas... the whispered secrets of the stars... unholy hexes of demon bones... and—"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Whaaaat? Why do you have to talk so funny all the time, Paimon doesn't understand!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Oz",
                    "T": "Our apologies, mein Fräulein is not well-versed in the parlance of the common folk."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Ooooh, so that's what you're for? To translate?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Oz",
                    "T": "I fear you misunderstand — I am no translator, but a humble conveyor of mein Fräulein's royal will. I would venture that what her <color=#00E1FFFF>Vision</color> is reacting to in this vicinity is, quite simply, <color=#00E1FFFF>elemental energy</color>."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Fischl",
                    "T": "Ahem, thank you, Oz. Those whose minds are muddled by the mundane matters of this woeful world are unable to fathom my noble intent as swiftly as thou art..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "So, there's elemental energy in the meteorite? And your Vision flashes in response to it?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "With a Vision, can you trace the elemental energy back to its source?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Shouldn't the source of the energy also respond in like fashion?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Paimon thinks... probably yes? Anyway, no harm in giving it a try! Let's look for <color=#00E1FFFF>shards of meteorite</color> using Fischl's <color=#00E1FFFF>Vision</color> — clearing them away will help make the area less dangerous."
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
