    "4111114": {
        "Desc": "Return to Springvale to check on the victims",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Edna! We got rid of the meteorite up on the hill behind the village. How are the victims doing now? Any better?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Edna",
                    "T": "Bless you! Thanks to your efforts, two of the victims have already awoken."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Hartman",
                    "T": "Ugh... I'm so sleepy... *yawn*"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Great, so it did work!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Edna",
                    "T": "I do hope you are able to dispose of the rest of the <color=#00E1FFFF>meteorites</color> around the village..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Then everyone else will wake up, too!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Oz",
                    "T": "This is wonderful news, it gladdens the heart."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Fischl",
                    "T": "Haha, it is most gladdening, indeed. Yet the news that I would be attending to this matter in person was surely the only guarantee that my faithful subjects ever needed of a felicitous outcome!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Hey, you just woke up, right? What were you dreaming about while you were asleep?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Hartman",
                    "T": "All I remember is that it was cold... I was walking along a <color=#00E1FFFF>mountain</color> path... In the ice and snow, I think..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "So... Just hiking in the mountains? Or were you supposed to have a destination?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Hartman",
                    "T": "Ah, I really don't know... In my dream, it felt like... I wasn't in full control of my actions."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Fischl",
                    "T": "Then thou wert surely cursed, I say! O, wretched scourge upon this land..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "(A curse? Could it really be?)"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Well, whatever the case, what we do know is that getting rid of the meteorite shards is helping. So, c'mon guys, we need to redouble our efforts!"
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
